{"body": "I agree with @bai. I appreciate that this is a good change, and that comparing strings isn't a good idea. But a *lot* of people are doing it anyway, and a *lot* of stuff breaks due to this change. I moved a project from beta1 to master and there were several gems who broke due to this.\r\n\r\nI understand if you want to introduce this change anyway, it's probably for the best, I just want to make sure you guys are aware of how disruptive this is.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/15508550", "created_at": "2013-03-27T07:26:36Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/8501#issuecomment-15508550", "updated_at": "2013-03-27T07:26:36Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 8501, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jnicklas/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jnicklas/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jnicklas/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/jnicklas", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jnicklas/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/jnicklas", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jnicklas/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/6c469749d725177dd2837d806c769cd4?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F02522a2b2726fb0a03bb19f2d8d9524d.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jnicklas/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jnicklas/received_events", "gravatar_id": "6c469749d725177dd2837d806c769cd4", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jnicklas/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "jnicklas", "type": "User", "id": 134, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jnicklas/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237f29abd3543c15100a65c"}, "id": 15508550, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/8501"}
